"<div>\n  <h3>Strawberry Tomato Juice with Mayonnaise Dressing</h3>\n  <p><em>Serves 2</em></p>\n  \n  <h4>Ingredients:</h4>\n  <ul>\n    <li>1 cup Tomato Juice</li>\n    <li>1 cup Strawberries</li>\n    <li>2 tablespoons Mayonnaise</li>\n    <li>1 tablespoon Honey</li>\n    <li>Crushed ice</li>\n  </ul>\n  \n  <h4>Instructions:</h4>\n  <ol>\n    <li>Blend the strawberries and tomato juice together until smooth.</li>\n    <li>Divide the crushed ice between two glasses.</li>\n    <li>Pour the strawberry tomato juice over the ice.</li>\n    <li>In a small bowl, mix together the mayonnaise and honey until well combined.</li>\n    <li>Drizzle the mayonnaise dressing over the top of the strawberry tomato juice.</li>\n    <li>Stir well before drinking.</li>\n  </ol>\n  \n  <h4>Enjoy your refreshing Strawberry Tomato Juice with Mayonnaise Dressing!</h4>\n</div>"